{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"65194-bunty-and-bubbly","title":"Bunty déteste se laver","description":"Bunty n'aime pas le savon. Elle refuse de se laver. Une nuit, elle fait un rêve. Que va-t-il se passer?","language":"French","langCode":"fr","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Sak Untala"],"illustrators":["Sorit Gupto"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/65194-bunty-and-bubbly"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size3/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/720260/size6/bfaca307e321a40d4fce0bf9bade9047.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2386/size6/9907217108246f4eb01c1ac7f252464b.jpg","text":"Bunty adore jouer avec des papillons...","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2387/size6/3cfef50c731271c06bc7df15adfad696.jpg","text":"...et avec des oiseaux.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2388/size6/0b2cc2ad4ba1e7c14ab8f85d1cc92a02.jpg","text":"Elle adore jouer avec des bateaux en papier.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2389/size6/1fea81780050ff2039ff47dedfb38216.jpg","text":"Elle aime aussi construire des châteaux de sable.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2390/size6/b4b058041a0f8816ef576bb510e2a358.jpg","text":"Quand Bunty rentre à la maison,\n \nsa maman lui demande de se laver.\nMais Bunty refuse.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2391/size6/f13b791f09d8c65688476d9d6782ede2.jpg","text":"«Je déteste les savons!» crie-t-elle.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2392/size6/45170485855b821bd3a27a6917664b6f.jpg","text":"Une nuit, elle fait un rêve dans lequel\ndes nuées de microbes viennent l'attaquer dans son château\n.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2393/size6/05cc5eb1bd0a44d4e01e16ad4432d8fd.jpg","text":"Bunty est poursuivie par les microbes.\n«Au secours! Au secours!»\nhurle-t-elle en essayant de se sauver.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2394/size6/c3075a8fd3d40bc48a3983ac434329a7.jpg","text":"Bubbly, le Roi des savons, apparaît soudain.\n«N'aie pas peur, Bunty,» dit-il.\n«À l'attaque!» ordonne-t-il à son armée de bulles de savon.\n«Sus aux microbes!»","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2395/size6/9e0c56e80240c4c4448a07ac8d9e80c0.jpg","text":"L'armée des bulles de savon parvient à chasser les microbes.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/2396/size6/342fa90cc8f644b89f8b05984faab025.jpg","text":"Bunty adore les savons, maintenant. Elle se brosse les dents et se lave toute seule.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":131}}